description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10-Minute Seated Dumbbell Strength Workout for Seniors' from the channel More Life Health Seniors.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
